## 10. Summary Checklist

Before submitting any new endpoint, verify:

- [ ] Controller injects service **interface**, not impl
- [ ] All responses wrapped in `ApiResponse<T>`
- [ ] Request DTO has `@Valid` + Jakarta validation annotations
- [ ] Service impl uses `@Transactional` / `@Transactional(readOnly = true)` correctly
- [ ] Repository always returns `Entity` or `Projection` — never called from Controller directly
- [ ] Repository queries always filter `isDeleted = false`
- [ ] Delete sets `isDeleted = true` — never calls `repository.delete()`
- [ ] Entity → DTO conversion done in ServiceImpl via `toResponse()` — no MapStruct
- [ ] `Page<Entity>` mapped via `.map(this::toResponse)` before returning from Service
- [ ] JOIN queries use Interface Projection (preferred) or DTO Projection — not full entity
- [ ] `ResourceNotFoundException` thrown when entity not found
- [ ] `GlobalExceptionHandler` covers the thrown exception type

